Package: QuadratiK
Type: Package
Title: Collection of methods constructed using the kernel-based quadratic distances
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2023-12-11
Author: Giovanni Saraceno <gsaracen@buffalo.edu> [aut, cre] (ORCID = 0000-0002-1753-2367),
         Marianthi Markatou [aut],
